BASICS:
  Every mobster has the following basic abilities to get started:
     mhelp      -  the Mobster help files
     mwho       -  listing of everyone currently on Nirvana
     mob        -  listing of all Mobsters currently logged on
     mob <str>  -  talk on the Mobster channel
     mob <:str> -  emote on the Mobster channel
     fam        -  listing of other family members (if joined)
     fam <str>  -  talk on your family channel (if joined)
     fam <:str> -  emote on your family channel (if joined)
